import React from 'react'
import './styles/App.css'
import { BrowserRouter } from 'react-router-dom'
import Navbar from './components/UI/navbar/Navbar'
import AppRouter from './components/UI/AppRouter'

function App() {
	return (
		<BrowserRouter>
			<Navbar />
			<AppRouter />
		</BrowserRouter>
	)
}

export default App
